1
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:39,950
[This Thriving Land]

2
00:01:40,330 --> 00:01:42,950
[Episode 18]

3
00:01:53,229 --> 00:01:54,000
How is she?

4
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:55,560
Is the baby safe?

5
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:58,490
Forgive my limited medical skills.

6
00:01:58,920 --> 00:01:59,840
Young Mistress

7
00:02:00,490 --> 00:02:01,420
is not pregnant.

8
00:02:03,430 --> 00:02:03,990
That's…

9
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,040
impossible.

10
00:02:07,210 --> 00:02:08,740
Did she have a miscarriage?

11
00:02:08,750 --> 00:02:10,030
Did you have a miscarriage?

12
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:10,470
She...

13
00:02:10,539 --> 00:02:11,700
She bled.

14
00:02:12,140 --> 00:02:13,140
Young Mistress

15
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,290
is not pregnant.

16
00:02:14,340 --> 00:02:16,470
And there are no signs of miscarriage.

17
00:02:16,470 --> 00:02:18,820
The bleeding is merely her period.

18
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,400
It can't be her period.

19
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:21,590
It can't be.

20
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:24,160
She hasn't had her period
for quite some time.

21
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:24,829
And look.

22
00:02:24,860 --> 00:02:25,350
She…

23
00:02:25,460 --> 00:02:27,570
she's showing.

24
00:02:28,710 --> 00:02:30,470
I've treated cases

25
00:02:30,490 --> 00:02:31,490
like this before.

26
00:02:32,030 --> 00:02:32,870
Some women

27
00:02:32,870 --> 00:02:35,030
believe they're pregnant,

28
00:02:35,250 --> 00:02:36,250
and their periods

29
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:38,030
stop due to that belief.

30
00:02:38,030 --> 00:02:38,960
On top of that,

31
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,520
staying in bed all day,

32
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,710
having multiple meals a day,

33
00:02:41,710 --> 00:02:42,640
and overeating,

34
00:02:43,079 --> 00:02:44,750
they start to look
as if they're pregnant.

35
00:02:44,750 --> 00:02:47,630
In truth, she's just put on weight.

36
00:02:48,590 --> 00:02:49,270
Madam,

37
00:02:49,550 --> 00:02:51,200
I'll take my leave now.

38
00:02:52,470 --> 00:02:53,420
I'll see him out.

39
00:03:03,030 --> 00:03:03,710
Qing.

40
00:03:05,470 --> 00:03:07,310
Bring Physician Huo here.

41
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:11,750
Qing!

42
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:14,120
Madam.

43
00:03:15,570 --> 00:03:17,570
Bring Physician Huo here.

44
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,240
Madam.

45
00:03:19,410 --> 00:03:20,880
When you asked me to find a physician,

46
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:22,760
I first tried to get Physician Huo,

47
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:24,040
but they told me

48
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:26,370
that he had returned to his home in town

49
00:03:26,750 --> 00:03:29,150
and hasn't been practicing
for a long time.

50
00:03:35,870 --> 00:03:37,280
I didn't mean it.

51
00:03:37,470 --> 00:03:39,310
I don't know what happened.

52
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,680
I've always thought this was strange.

53
00:03:57,870 --> 00:03:59,270
It never made sense to me.

54
00:03:59,710 --> 00:04:01,110
So that's what happened.

55
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:05,020
I didn't want to get involved.

56
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:07,910
With permanent tenancy,
I don't want any more trouble.

57
00:04:07,910 --> 00:04:09,680
But I can't just ignore it.

58
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:13,480
If the land were taken back again…

59
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,750
What should I do about this?

60
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,560
There's no point asking you.

61
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:25,020
You'll just take
your father's side anyway.

62
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,220
If that's what you really think,

63
00:04:27,220 --> 00:04:28,880
don't bother asking me at all.

64
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,470
Xiuxiu,

65
00:04:34,750 --> 00:04:35,720
do you have any ideas?

66
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,720
Please help me.

67
00:04:38,270 --> 00:04:39,720
I don't want to quit.

68
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,920
L-Look at you,

69
00:04:42,430 --> 00:04:43,600
totally at a loss.

70
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:45,630
You threw a fit as soon as you walked in.

71
00:04:45,630 --> 00:04:47,310
How could you call her Ning Xiuxiu?

72
00:04:47,310 --> 00:04:48,830
Apologize to her now,

73
00:04:48,950 --> 00:04:51,210
so she'll help you figure something out.

74
00:04:56,630 --> 00:04:59,510
X-Xiuxiu, I'm sorry.

75
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,390
What?

76
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,610
You want to quit?

77
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,070
Maybe

78
00:05:14,870 --> 00:05:15,830
Dajiao should be the head

79
00:05:15,830 --> 00:05:17,490
of the Farmers' Association.

80
00:05:17,870 --> 00:05:19,720
You're literate and can help him.

81
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:20,720
I can't even read.

82
00:05:22,270 --> 00:05:24,070
What does this say?

83
00:05:25,190 --> 00:05:26,560
I've been busy working in the fields

84
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:27,760
and forgotten it all.

85
00:05:29,510 --> 00:05:31,910
I don't know
how to deal with Ning Xuexiang.

86
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,040
Kejin.

87
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,159
Kejin.

88
00:05:45,550 --> 00:05:46,840
Tietou from the Farmers' Association
is here,

89
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:47,840
asking to see you.

90
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:50,080
What does he want with me?

91
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:52,750
I saw him carrying
the Farmers' Association flag,

92
00:05:52,750 --> 00:05:54,510
so it's probably about the association.

93
00:05:54,510 --> 00:05:56,110
How many people did he bring?

94
00:05:56,190 --> 00:05:57,270
Just himself.

95
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,720
Send him in.

96
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:00,920
Okay.

97
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,310
Tietou,

98
00:06:08,250 --> 00:06:09,380
you needed to see me?

99
00:06:14,460 --> 00:06:15,780
You're a literate man.

100
00:06:17,510 --> 00:06:19,070
I've memorized

101
00:06:19,070 --> 00:06:20,930
every single word of this letter.

102
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:22,870
Take a close look.

103
00:06:24,110 --> 00:06:27,640
If Ning Xuexiang dares
to fool the Farmers' Association again…

104
00:06:32,630 --> 00:06:35,520
the county farmers' association
will deal with him.

105
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:36,680
What happens then?

106
00:06:37,990 --> 00:06:39,450
That'll be out of my hands.

107
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,300
I'll take my leave now.

108
00:07:11,230 --> 00:07:13,960
What happens
if the farmers' association comes?

109
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:18,380
When they arrested
Zhang Zongchang's county magistrate,

110
00:07:18,390 --> 00:07:19,520
they used handcuffs

111
00:07:19,750 --> 00:07:21,080
and tied him up tightly.

112
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,190
Son,

113
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:32,750
is there no way for me to escape this?

114
00:07:35,159 --> 00:07:38,120
Tietou dared
to come to me alone with a flag.

115
00:07:39,310 --> 00:07:41,800
He must have a mastermind behind him.

116
00:07:42,630 --> 00:07:43,760
But this mastermind

117
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,530
has left you some room to maneuver.

118
00:07:46,950 --> 00:07:50,680
Otherwise, Tietou would've gone straight
to the county farmers' association,

119
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:52,070
and we'd have no way out.

120
00:08:06,270 --> 00:08:06,950
Kuangzi.

121
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:11,240
Master.

122
00:08:11,950 --> 00:08:12,430
Go.

123
00:08:13,870 --> 00:08:15,800
Fetch Tietou for me.

124
00:08:16,950 --> 00:08:17,750
Tell him

125
00:08:18,270 --> 00:08:20,830
I have important matters
to discuss with him.

126
00:08:43,900 --> 00:08:44,700
Young Master.

127
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:48,840
Madam said she has no appetite

128
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:49,680
and doesn't want it in her room.

129
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:51,210
She asked me to bring it out.

130
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,270
What about Young Mistress?

131
00:08:55,270 --> 00:08:56,240
She ate

132
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,720
and then kept crying.

133
00:09:00,970 --> 00:09:01,960
You may go now.

134
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,080
Xiuxiu.

135
00:09:19,510 --> 00:09:20,080
Xiuxiu.

136
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:22,220
You're really something else!

137
00:09:22,220 --> 00:09:24,070
I'm totally impressed.

138
00:09:25,790 --> 00:09:26,720
What's with you?

139
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,600
What did Xiuxiu do?

140
00:09:28,870 --> 00:09:30,910
Dajiao, let me finish.

141
00:09:31,790 --> 00:09:32,320
Xiuxiu,

142
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:35,200
didn't you ask me
to give that letter to your brother?

143
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,840
I had been uneasy about it,

144
00:09:37,060 --> 00:09:37,970
constantly worried.

145
00:09:37,970 --> 00:09:39,230
That's treasure to me.

146
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:41,610
Whether I eat, sleep,
or work in the fields,

147
00:09:41,610 --> 00:09:43,970
I keep it in this pouch
my mother sewed for me.

148
00:09:43,970 --> 00:09:45,630
How could I just give it to him?

149
00:09:46,060 --> 00:09:47,120
But unexpectedly,

150
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:48,880
your fathe...

151
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:49,650
I mean...

152
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:50,900
Ning Xuexiang…

153
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,020
he actually

154
00:09:53,190 --> 00:09:54,000
returned the letter to me

155
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:55,550
very respectfully.

156
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:57,370
He even treated me to drinks

157
00:09:57,370 --> 00:09:58,960
and toasted me three times in a row.

158
00:09:58,960 --> 00:09:59,420
Dajiao.

159
00:09:59,670 --> 00:10:02,200
Ning Xuexiang toasted me
three times in a row.

160
00:10:04,660 --> 00:10:05,910
What about the tenancy?

161
00:10:05,910 --> 00:10:07,390
I almost forgot the most important part.

162
00:10:07,390 --> 00:10:08,270
I asked around.

163
00:10:09,150 --> 00:10:10,790
They said those families
with fake permanent tenancies

164
00:10:10,790 --> 00:10:12,650
got real ones from Ning Xuexiang.

165
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:13,870
Even Glutton Fei

166
00:10:13,870 --> 00:10:15,470
got a permanent tenancy too.

167
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:17,650
I also went to Mrs. Fei's place.

168
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:18,720
They said she was sick,

169
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:20,190
so I had Qing pass on the message.

170
00:10:20,190 --> 00:10:20,950
Qing said

171
00:10:21,270 --> 00:10:22,080
Mrs. Fei told me

172
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,480
to farm my land with peace of mind.

173
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,610
She won't take away my land ever again.

174
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:26,770
Xiuxiu,

175
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,480
I'm really grateful to you.

176
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,480
Thank you so much.

177
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,740
Well, that's perfect.

178
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:34,080
Hurry back to your hut
and check on things

179
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,940
in case it's snatched away again.

180
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:37,670
No way, no way.

181
00:10:38,650 --> 00:10:40,310
No one's taking my land again.

182
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:41,910
Alright, Dajiao, Xiuxiu,

183
00:10:41,910 --> 00:10:43,200
you two carry on with your business.

184
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,660
I'm heading to the fields.

185
00:10:45,650 --> 00:10:46,710
Thank you, Xiuxiu.

186
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,480
What did you do?

187
00:10:57,820 --> 00:10:59,780
I thought something was fishy about this.

188
00:10:59,780 --> 00:11:01,860
Sure enough, they were hiding something.

189
00:11:01,860 --> 00:11:03,920
Tietou's bluff flushed it right out.

190
00:11:05,550 --> 00:11:06,670
B-But…

191
00:11:06,670 --> 00:11:09,000
won't your father come after you for this?

192
00:11:09,390 --> 00:11:10,200
Let him come.

193
00:11:10,870 --> 00:11:12,670
I have questions for him anyway.

194
00:11:13,150 --> 00:11:14,600
This feud between you two—

195
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:16,150
when will it ever end?

196
00:11:19,390 --> 00:11:20,520
I'll go back to work.

197
00:11:32,380 --> 00:11:33,270
Fei Wendian!

198
00:11:34,910 --> 00:11:35,270
Susu.

199
00:11:35,270 --> 00:11:36,030
Come with me.

200
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:37,630
Where to?

201
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:39,240
Don't sleep here anymore.

202
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,390
Sleep with me in my room.

203
00:11:40,390 --> 00:11:40,870
Susu.

204
00:11:42,630 --> 00:11:43,960
What are you doing?

205
00:11:45,700 --> 00:11:48,150
It's not my fault I'm not pregnant.

206
00:11:48,670 --> 00:11:50,120
I really thought I was.

207
00:11:50,670 --> 00:11:52,630
Besides, getting pregnant
isn't that hard.

208
00:11:52,630 --> 00:11:53,720
Your sister-in-law is

209
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,840
acting like I'll never get pregnant again!

210
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:56,970
I've made up my mind.

211
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:57,810
She blames me

212
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,440
because I'm not pregnant.

213
00:11:59,780 --> 00:12:00,910
I didn't get pregnant this time,

214
00:12:00,910 --> 00:12:02,120
but I will next time.

215
00:12:02,270 --> 00:12:02,790
Let's go.

216
00:12:02,790 --> 00:12:03,670
Go back to my room with me.

217
00:12:03,670 --> 00:12:04,720
Don't stay here.

218
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:06,440
Let's go!

219
00:12:07,390 --> 00:12:08,110
Susu.

220
00:12:08,510 --> 00:12:09,720
Calm down.

221
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,500
This isn't something to rush.

222
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:20,150
We can't keep making the same mistake.

223
00:12:37,750 --> 00:12:38,550
Young Master.

224
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:41,520
How is my sister-in-law?

225
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,360
Come in.

226
00:12:46,510 --> 00:12:47,200
Xiaoqin.

227
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:49,050
Go get some food for her.

228
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,120
Yes.

229
00:12:56,200 --> 00:12:57,130
Sister-in-law,

230
00:12:57,630 --> 00:12:59,440
you haven't eaten anything all day.

231
00:12:59,440 --> 00:13:00,770
Your body can't take it.

232
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,000
Every time I think of this,

233
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:05,800
I feel a stabbing pain in my ribs.

234
00:13:06,510 --> 00:13:07,480
I can't eat.

235
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:11,130
Sister-in-law,

236
00:13:11,550 --> 00:13:13,720
if you're feeling unwell,
you should see a doctor.

237
00:13:13,720 --> 00:13:15,050
Don't just tough it out.

238
00:13:15,630 --> 00:13:16,670
I'm fine.

239
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:18,720
I know

240
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:20,600
I'm just mad.

241
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:25,410
Sister-in-law,

242
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:27,910
Susu didn't mean it.

243
00:13:28,150 --> 00:13:29,320
Please forgive her.

244
00:13:29,870 --> 00:13:31,440
Do I need you to tell me that?

245
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:34,120
You can go now.

246
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:36,130
Sister-in-law,

247
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:38,200
well,

248
00:13:38,790 --> 00:13:40,450
I'll head back to school then.

249
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,200
Back to school?

250
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:43,970
Why are you leaving?

251
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,080
There's a lot

252
00:13:46,470 --> 00:13:47,990
I need to handle there.

253
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:53,020
Susu doesn't need me around anymore.

254
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:56,720
Go, then.

255
00:13:58,160 --> 00:13:59,870
I know I can't make you stay.

256
00:14:06,630 --> 00:14:07,560
Sister-in-law,

257
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,360
take care.

258
00:14:37,390 --> 00:14:38,000
Susu,

259
00:14:39,190 --> 00:14:40,310
I'm leaving soon,

260
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:43,730
going back to school
for some important matters.

261
00:14:44,750 --> 00:14:45,910
I'll say it again:

262
00:14:46,870 --> 00:14:48,630
what we had was wrong from the beginning.

263
00:14:48,630 --> 00:14:50,360
You have a bright future ahead.

264
00:14:51,060 --> 00:14:53,060
You need to make plans for yourself.

265
00:15:06,390 --> 00:15:07,030
Qing.

266
00:15:07,910 --> 00:15:08,510
Let's go.

267
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:29,320
Wendian.

268
00:15:31,840 --> 00:15:33,200
Fei Wendian!

269
00:15:38,750 --> 00:15:40,120
He just left.

270
00:15:41,670 --> 00:15:43,030
He just left like that.

271
00:15:58,390 --> 00:16:00,790
I knew Tietou wasn't
smart enough for this.

272
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:02,320
After a few drinks,

273
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:04,330
I got the whole story out of him.

274
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:08,240
Turns out Mrs. Fei was behind it all.

275
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:10,240
That woman is so calculating.

276
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:14,990
I told you
a mastermind was behind Tietou,

277
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:17,370
but I never thought it would be her.

278
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:21,270
Father,

279
00:16:21,670 --> 00:16:23,670
we need to think this through.

280
00:16:23,690 --> 00:16:25,690
Susu is still at her place after all.

281
00:16:25,790 --> 00:16:26,910
Father.

282
00:16:27,520 --> 00:16:27,980
Father.

283
00:16:28,270 --> 00:16:28,870
Kejin.

284
00:16:29,550 --> 00:16:30,120
Father.

285
00:16:30,390 --> 00:16:31,840
I can't stay at the Fei Residence anymore.

286
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:33,170
I want to come back home.

287
00:16:33,620 --> 00:16:34,900
Susu, sit down.

288
00:16:36,390 --> 00:16:38,630
Well, speak of the devil.

289
00:16:39,150 --> 00:16:41,980
You should be resting properly
for childbirth there

290
00:16:41,980 --> 00:16:44,240
instead of coming back here all the time.

291
00:16:45,840 --> 00:16:46,840
I'm not pregnant.

292
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:47,550
What?

293
00:16:49,910 --> 00:16:50,840
What's going on?

294
00:16:51,060 --> 00:16:53,180
I don't know. I just...

295
00:16:54,240 --> 00:16:56,390
I can't explain it all at once.

296
00:16:56,390 --> 00:16:57,390
Anyway, Mrs. Fei

297
00:16:57,390 --> 00:16:59,270
stopped talking to me
after she found out I wasn't pregnant.

298
00:16:59,270 --> 00:17:01,030
The meals are barely edible!

299
00:17:01,030 --> 00:17:03,360
I can't stay at the Fei Residence anymore!

300
00:17:03,670 --> 00:17:05,000
What about Fei Wendian?

301
00:17:05,240 --> 00:17:05,880
He's gone.

302
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:06,650
He's gone?

303
00:17:06,670 --> 00:17:07,589
What did I say?

304
00:17:08,790 --> 00:17:09,960
She tricked me

305
00:17:10,270 --> 00:17:11,670
and bullied your sister.

306
00:17:12,550 --> 00:17:13,750
I'll stand up for you.

307
00:17:13,960 --> 00:17:14,589
This time,

308
00:17:15,720 --> 00:17:17,109
we'll settle all scores with Widow Fei,

309
00:17:17,109 --> 00:17:19,349
both old and new!

310
00:17:25,589 --> 00:17:26,050
Dajiao.

311
00:17:26,480 --> 00:17:27,960
You're leaving again?

312
00:17:28,240 --> 00:17:28,920
Yeah.

313
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:30,800
It's a time of unrest.

314
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:33,240
I've got to make some money
while I still can.

315
00:17:33,240 --> 00:17:34,560
If one day I can't go out,

316
00:17:34,560 --> 00:17:36,110
the whole village will run out of salt.

317
00:17:36,110 --> 00:17:38,110
The burden on my shoulders is heavy.

318
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:41,070
You brought back a lot of goods this time.

319
00:17:41,070 --> 00:17:42,870
I spent months collecting them.

320
00:17:43,670 --> 00:17:44,270
This time,

321
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:46,510
I'm going on a long journey.

322
00:17:46,510 --> 00:17:48,400
It'll take over 10 days, right?

323
00:17:48,540 --> 00:17:50,390
About half a month.

324
00:17:54,510 --> 00:17:56,640
Press gangs! Press gangs!

325
00:17:56,960 --> 00:17:58,280
Stay there! Don't run!

326
00:17:59,110 --> 00:17:59,590
Don't run!

327
00:17:59,590 --> 00:18:00,200
Run!

328
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:01,480
Dajiao, run! It's the press gangs!

329
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:02,920
Nobody move! Hurry up!

330
00:18:03,200 --> 00:18:05,110
Where are you running? Are you stupid?

331
00:18:05,110 --> 00:18:05,640
Hurry up!

332
00:18:06,270 --> 00:18:07,440
All of you, stop running!

333
00:18:07,440 --> 00:18:08,000
Stop there!

334
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:08,440
All you young men…

335
00:18:08,440 --> 00:18:09,030
Hurry up!

336
00:18:09,030 --> 00:18:10,110
Play dumb and deaf.

337
00:18:10,680 --> 00:18:11,920
Sign up now!

338
00:18:12,310 --> 00:18:13,920
You can eat well, drink well,

339
00:18:14,440 --> 00:18:15,240
and…

340
00:18:16,350 --> 00:18:17,550
and get military pay.

341
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:18,650
Give it to me.

342
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:24,120
People of Ox Temple Village, listen up!

343
00:18:24,590 --> 00:18:26,050
All able-bodied young men

344
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:28,920
should go to the village entrance
to sign up right now.

345
00:18:28,920 --> 00:18:30,580
Wages will be paid on the spot.

346
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:32,450
If anyone tries to escape,

347
00:18:32,450 --> 00:18:34,380
his whole family will be punished!

348
00:18:34,400 --> 00:18:36,600
Your village chief failed to do his job.

349
00:18:36,880 --> 00:18:39,110
We required one man from each household,

350
00:18:39,110 --> 00:18:40,270
and he came up short.

351
00:18:40,640 --> 00:18:41,240
Soon,

352
00:18:41,400 --> 00:18:43,400
I'll take him back for questioning.

353
00:18:43,510 --> 00:18:44,310
Take him away.

354
00:18:45,070 --> 00:18:47,000
Move! Don't run, or I'll shoot you!

355
00:18:47,340 --> 00:18:48,620
Get up! Move!

356
00:18:48,790 --> 00:18:49,590
Move!

357
00:18:50,590 --> 00:18:51,000
You!

358
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:52,560
Come here!

359
00:18:53,920 --> 00:18:54,780
How old are you?

360
00:18:54,880 --> 00:18:56,360
I-I'm just 15.

361
00:18:56,740 --> 00:18:58,830
It's true. He just turned 15.

362
00:19:00,660 --> 00:19:01,190
Get lost!

363
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:06,110
You two!

364
00:19:06,440 --> 00:19:07,110
Don't move!

365
00:19:14,590 --> 00:19:15,030
You,

366
00:19:15,510 --> 00:19:16,240
turn around.

367
00:19:17,160 --> 00:19:17,890
Turn around!

368
00:19:21,710 --> 00:19:22,920
He's disabled.

369
00:19:23,550 --> 00:19:24,350
A hunchback.

370
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:26,680
He's had this condition since childhood.

371
00:19:26,680 --> 00:19:28,610
Even sleeping on a door panel
didn't fix it.

372
00:19:28,610 --> 00:19:30,240
He can't farm or carry a gun.

373
00:19:31,200 --> 00:19:32,860
He can only do small business.

374
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:38,680
A hunchback?

375
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:40,480
Let me see.

376
00:19:46,440 --> 00:19:48,240
You really are a hunchback.

377
00:19:52,070 --> 00:19:52,480
You.

378
00:19:55,240 --> 00:19:56,300
I'm talking to you.

379
00:19:58,140 --> 00:19:59,580
This is my brother.

380
00:20:00,030 --> 00:20:02,310
He's deaf and dumb. Even if…

381
00:20:02,780 --> 00:20:04,800
a cannon fired next to his ear,

382
00:20:05,720 --> 00:20:06,850
he wouldn't hear it.

383
00:20:07,560 --> 00:20:08,230
A deaf man?

384
00:20:09,030 --> 00:20:09,830
Yes.

385
00:20:09,970 --> 00:20:11,290
He's his legs,

386
00:20:11,750 --> 00:20:14,070
and he's his ears and mouth.

387
00:20:14,560 --> 00:20:16,560
They work together to make a living.

388
00:20:32,770 --> 00:20:34,290
He really is deaf.

389
00:20:36,440 --> 00:20:38,200
Truly deaf and dumb.

390
00:20:40,590 --> 00:20:41,190
Let's go!

391
00:20:54,200 --> 00:20:55,120
Run! Run!

392
00:20:57,640 --> 00:20:58,700
What are you doing?

393
00:20:59,240 --> 00:21:00,370
Are you really deaf?

394
00:21:00,600 --> 00:21:01,310
Run!

395
00:21:05,430 --> 00:21:06,510
I-I can hear you!

396
00:21:08,110 --> 00:21:08,750
Oh, no.

397
00:21:09,140 --> 00:21:10,450
You can't go back now.

398
00:21:10,480 --> 00:21:11,610
Now I see.

399
00:21:11,960 --> 00:21:14,200
Heaven sent me here today to help you.

400
00:21:17,090 --> 00:21:17,590
Listen,

401
00:21:17,960 --> 00:21:18,440
Dajiao,

402
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:19,810
I don't mind taking you along.

403
00:21:19,810 --> 00:21:21,480
Come with me for half a month.

404
00:21:22,400 --> 00:21:23,570
I know what kind of man you are—

405
00:21:23,570 --> 00:21:25,130
you don't cause trouble,

406
00:21:25,150 --> 00:21:26,200
and you're a good helper.

407
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:27,260
After half a month,

408
00:21:27,360 --> 00:21:28,560
you'll get some cash.

409
00:21:28,830 --> 00:21:29,480
How about that?

410
00:21:29,480 --> 00:21:30,440
That won't work.

411
00:21:30,830 --> 00:21:32,470
My parents and Xiuxiu

412
00:21:32,790 --> 00:21:34,640
will worry if they can't find me.

413
00:21:36,070 --> 00:21:37,550
Are you afraid you'll miss your wife

414
00:21:37,550 --> 00:21:38,880
or afraid to leave home?

415
00:21:39,510 --> 00:21:41,200
If you really were a weak man,

416
00:21:41,720 --> 00:21:43,350
your wife wouldn't have married you.

417
00:21:43,350 --> 00:21:44,550
Don't look down on me.

418
00:21:44,680 --> 00:21:46,410
I'm not afraid of leaving home.

419
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:49,360
I just don't want them to worry about me.

420
00:21:51,880 --> 00:21:53,550
When we were together just now,

421
00:21:53,550 --> 00:21:54,800
your second uncle saw us.

422
00:21:54,800 --> 00:21:57,000
He'll definitely tell Xiuxiu about it.

423
00:21:57,380 --> 00:21:59,910
If it's really a problem,
we'll head into town

424
00:21:59,960 --> 00:22:02,160
and have someone send a message for you.

425
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:05,730
Stop hesitating.
You'll be caught if you go back!

426
00:22:07,270 --> 00:22:08,800
Come on, let's go. Hurry!

427
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:18,060
What's happening?

428
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:20,110
W-What's going on?

429
00:22:20,110 --> 00:22:20,400
Nothing.

430
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:21,030
-Auntie.
-Hurry up!

431
00:22:21,030 --> 00:22:22,590
Auntie, what's happening?

432
00:22:22,590 --> 00:22:24,400
Those soldiers are crazy.

433
00:22:24,400 --> 00:22:26,530
They're taking any young man they see.

434
00:22:30,810 --> 00:22:31,920
Zhuzi, Zhuzi!

435
00:22:32,430 --> 00:22:33,070
Take this.

436
00:22:33,410 --> 00:22:33,830
I don't need it.

437
00:22:33,830 --> 00:22:34,550
Be careful.

438
00:22:34,550 --> 00:22:35,200
Tietou.

439
00:22:35,880 --> 00:22:36,330
Xiuxiu.

440
00:22:36,330 --> 00:22:37,530
Have you seen Dajiao?

441
00:22:37,790 --> 00:22:39,550
No. When did he leave?

442
00:22:39,570 --> 00:22:41,440
He went to the fields early this morning.

443
00:22:41,440 --> 00:22:42,830
There's nobody in the fields now.

444
00:22:42,830 --> 00:22:44,240
They said press gangs came from the west,

445
00:22:44,240 --> 00:22:45,110
taking every man they saw.

446
00:22:45,110 --> 00:22:46,400
We can only go to the back mountain.

447
00:22:46,400 --> 00:22:48,200
There are press gangs there too.

448
00:22:48,480 --> 00:22:49,640
Let's head east of the village.

449
00:22:49,640 --> 00:22:49,950
Okay.

450
00:22:49,950 --> 00:22:50,480
Let's go.

451
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:51,480
Xiuxiu,

452
00:22:51,780 --> 00:22:53,090
where are you going to look for Dajiao?

453
00:22:53,090 --> 00:22:54,200
I'm going to find Kejin

454
00:22:54,200 --> 00:22:56,460
to get some militia men to help me search.

455
00:22:56,640 --> 00:22:57,170
Let's go.

456
00:22:57,790 --> 00:22:58,250
Tietou.

457
00:22:58,750 --> 00:22:59,350
What?

458
00:23:00,350 --> 00:23:01,150
That's right.

459
00:23:01,810 --> 00:23:04,010
The recruiters don't take militia men.

460
00:23:04,750 --> 00:23:05,310
Let's go.

461
00:23:24,550 --> 00:23:25,270
Kejin!

462
00:23:25,580 --> 00:23:26,180
Kejin!

463
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:27,920
Xiuxiu.

464
00:23:27,920 --> 00:23:28,320
Kejin.

465
00:23:28,590 --> 00:23:29,520
Why are you here?

466
00:23:29,680 --> 00:23:30,480
The press gangs

467
00:23:30,480 --> 00:23:31,680
are taking young men.

468
00:23:31,830 --> 00:23:33,440
I can't find Dajiao anywhere.

469
00:23:33,440 --> 00:23:34,880
Can you get some men
to help me look for him?

470
00:23:34,880 --> 00:23:35,540
Don't panic.

471
00:23:35,540 --> 00:23:37,490
My men can't go out now either.

472
00:23:37,750 --> 00:23:39,350
I've already pulled everyone
off the fortress.

473
00:23:39,350 --> 00:23:40,350
How about this?

474
00:23:40,350 --> 00:23:41,310
Once they are gone,

475
00:23:41,310 --> 00:23:42,070
I'll send men to find him.

476
00:23:42,070 --> 00:23:44,240
That will be too late.

477
00:23:44,240 --> 00:23:46,570
I caught these two
climbing over the wall.

478
00:23:47,030 --> 00:23:49,750
What are you doing?
We're all from this village.

479
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:51,400
We all know each other.

480
00:23:52,240 --> 00:23:53,720
Kejin, Kejin, look.

481
00:23:54,140 --> 00:23:55,660
Enough. Let them go!

482
00:23:55,920 --> 00:23:56,580
Let go of me!

483
00:23:57,480 --> 00:23:58,160
Kejin,

484
00:23:58,640 --> 00:23:59,110
well,

485
00:23:59,440 --> 00:24:00,590
you gotta help us out.

486
00:24:00,590 --> 00:24:01,550
Let us hide here.

487
00:24:01,790 --> 00:24:02,590
How can I help?

488
00:24:02,960 --> 00:24:03,680
Where can you hide?

489
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:04,350
Just look around.

490
00:24:04,350 --> 00:24:06,080
Where could you possibly hide?

491
00:24:06,350 --> 00:24:07,680
Don't worry about that.

492
00:24:08,480 --> 00:24:09,410
I'll hide there.

493
00:24:13,590 --> 00:24:14,920
What are you doing here?

494
00:24:15,230 --> 00:24:16,690
When did you sneak in here?

495
00:24:17,400 --> 00:24:18,590
Didn't anyone notice this boy

496
00:24:18,590 --> 00:24:19,440
hiding here?

497
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:22,030
What good are you?

498
00:24:22,510 --> 00:24:23,400
Close the door!

499
00:24:26,680 --> 00:24:27,110
Besides,

500
00:24:27,110 --> 00:24:28,640
why are you all hiding here?

501
00:24:29,030 --> 00:24:31,290
I don't have any magic tricks to hide you.

502
00:24:31,680 --> 00:24:33,340
What if those soldiers decide

503
00:24:33,350 --> 00:24:34,660
to come into this courtyard?

504
00:24:34,660 --> 00:24:36,240
Not only will you get caught,

505
00:24:36,240 --> 00:24:38,310
but all my boys will be implicated too.

506
00:24:38,310 --> 00:24:40,240
Hurry. Go back where you came from!

507
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:42,200
We have no choice, do we?

508
00:24:42,790 --> 00:24:44,160
If it weren't for the press gangs,

509
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:46,090
we wouldn't set foot in your place.

510
00:24:48,510 --> 00:24:50,240
Just looking at you annoys me.

511
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:53,160
Back then, I thought you were strong

512
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:54,720
and asked you to join the militia,

513
00:24:54,720 --> 00:24:56,790
but you wouldn't, no matter what I said.

514
00:24:56,790 --> 00:24:57,200
What?

515
00:24:57,700 --> 00:24:59,960
My militia
doesn't look so worthless now, huh?

516
00:24:59,960 --> 00:25:01,560
Aren't you Director Tietou?

517
00:25:01,680 --> 00:25:03,270
You're the director.
What are you afraid of?

518
00:25:03,270 --> 00:25:04,240
Who would dare take you?

519
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:05,350
C-Cut the crap!

520
00:25:05,970 --> 00:25:08,050
We just need to hide here for now.

521
00:25:08,110 --> 00:25:08,960
Yes or no?

522
00:25:08,960 --> 00:25:09,590
No!

523
00:25:13,400 --> 00:25:14,160
Get up!

524
00:25:14,750 --> 00:25:16,230
It hurts!

525
00:25:16,230 --> 00:25:17,550
You're still wet behind the ears.

526
00:25:17,550 --> 00:25:18,110
Who would want you?

527
00:25:18,110 --> 00:25:18,590
It hurts.

528
00:25:18,590 --> 00:25:20,070
The officers wouldn't take you
even if you volunteered.

529
00:25:20,070 --> 00:25:21,830
They say they can't fill the quota,

530
00:25:21,830 --> 00:25:23,490
so they'll take children too.

531
00:25:23,550 --> 00:25:25,070
It hurts.

532
00:25:27,960 --> 00:25:29,590
What a chaotic world.

533
00:25:30,290 --> 00:25:31,240
I can't help you.

534
00:25:31,350 --> 00:25:32,680
Go back where you came from.

535
00:25:32,680 --> 00:25:33,070
Move, move!

536
00:25:33,070 --> 00:25:33,680
Kejin,

537
00:25:34,110 --> 00:25:35,720
please help them.

538
00:25:35,880 --> 00:25:37,070
Where else can they hide?

539
00:25:37,070 --> 00:25:39,310
Xiuxiu, I can't help them.

540
00:25:39,310 --> 00:25:40,790
All my men here

541
00:25:40,790 --> 00:25:43,120
have already been registered.

542
00:25:43,200 --> 00:25:44,680
Names matched to faces.

543
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:46,030
Report: no one here.

544
00:25:46,030 --> 00:25:46,830
No one?

545
00:25:46,830 --> 00:25:47,960
Report: no one here.

546
00:25:48,830 --> 00:25:49,480
No one?

547
00:25:49,480 --> 00:25:50,030
No.

548
00:25:50,210 --> 00:25:52,010
Come. Let's go check that house.

549
00:25:52,590 --> 00:25:54,240
Besides, when the soldiers come,

550
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:55,440
they don't take men here

551
00:25:55,440 --> 00:25:57,240
because Father and I paid them off.

552
00:25:57,240 --> 00:25:58,550
So stay out of this.

553
00:25:58,570 --> 00:25:59,000
Xiu.

554
00:26:00,070 --> 00:26:00,640
Open up!

555
00:26:03,960 --> 00:26:04,510
Open up!

556
00:26:06,590 --> 00:26:07,240
Open up!

557
00:26:07,240 --> 00:26:08,400
Coming, coming.

558
00:26:11,400 --> 00:26:12,110
Officer.

559
00:26:13,270 --> 00:26:14,000
You're here.

560
00:26:14,630 --> 00:26:15,490
Please come in.

561
00:26:16,960 --> 00:26:18,370
Everyone, stop training.

562
00:26:18,370 --> 00:26:20,100
The officer is here. Greet him.

563
00:26:20,200 --> 00:26:21,640
Good morning, Officer.

564
00:26:21,960 --> 00:26:22,550
Officer,

565
00:26:23,090 --> 00:26:24,020
are you thirsty?

566
00:26:24,200 --> 00:26:25,400
I'll get you some tea.

567
00:26:30,120 --> 00:26:31,250
Come here, Officer.

568
00:26:36,550 --> 00:26:37,080
Officer,

569
00:26:37,440 --> 00:26:38,240
have some tea.

570
00:26:41,510 --> 00:26:42,310
What's wrong?

571
00:26:42,830 --> 00:26:43,440
What's wrong?

572
00:26:43,440 --> 00:26:44,770
What kind of tea is this?

573
00:26:45,930 --> 00:26:47,390
I'll get you some good tea.

574
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:48,400
Xiu!

575
00:26:48,830 --> 00:26:50,830
Bring some good tea for the officer.

576
