602
00:27:53,710 --> 00:27:54,900
Every name matches,

603
00:27:55,010 --> 00:27:56,180
all on the register.

604
00:27:56,350 --> 00:27:56,880
They're all here?

605
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:58,310
Everyone's here, Officer.

606
00:27:58,310 --> 00:27:58,880
Officer.

607
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:02,620
Take this for some drinks.

608
00:28:03,830 --> 00:28:04,440
They're all here, huh?

609
00:28:04,440 --> 00:28:05,510
Yeah, yeah.

610
00:28:06,200 --> 00:28:06,680
Hurry.

611
00:28:06,880 --> 00:28:07,440
