615
00:28:14,790 --> 00:28:15,920
for your next visit.

616
00:28:16,280 --> 00:28:16,720
Okay.

617
00:28:16,880 --> 00:28:17,830
See the officer out.

618
00:28:17,830 --> 00:28:18,440
This way.

619
00:28:18,440 --> 00:28:19,880
Farewell, Officer.

620
00:28:44,570 --> 00:28:45,310
