630
00:29:06,590 --> 00:29:08,750
He said when I came here,

631
00:29:08,750 --> 00:29:10,220
I should take attendance first

632
00:29:10,220 --> 00:29:12,220
and then make a copy of the register.

633
00:29:13,350 --> 00:29:14,680
