635
00:29:16,960 --> 00:29:17,490
Alright.

636
00:29:17,780 --> 00:29:19,900
Go get the register.

637
00:29:23,830 --> 00:29:24,440
Go.

638
00:29:24,740 --> 00:29:26,220
Bring me the register.

639
