687
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:55,320
Now it's nowhere

688
00:30:55,320 --> 00:30:56,460
to be found.

689
00:30:56,680 --> 00:30:57,590
Go find it!

690
00:30:59,270 --> 00:30:59,680
Go!

691
00:31:05,790 --> 00:31:06,680
X-Xiuxiu.

692
00:31:11,510 --> 00:31:12,160
Fei Wu!

693
00:31:12,830 --> 00:31:13,790
Have you found it?

694
00:31:13,790 --> 00:31:14,510
Yes!

695
00:31:15,340 --> 00:31:15,830
Boss.

696
00:31:15,830 --> 00:31:16,590
Let me see it.

697
00:31:18,170 --> 00:31:18,960
Is this it?

698
00:31:21,270 --> 00:31:21,680
Look.

699
00:31:21,930 --> 00:31:23,190
He found it. Here it is.

700
00:31:26,830 --> 00:31:27,590
Huang Yinhe.

701
00:31:28,110 --> 00:31:28,640
Present.

702
00:31:30,350 --> 00:31:31,210
Ning Yousheng.

703
00:31:31,270 --> 00:31:31,800
Present.

