00:31:33,310 --> 00:31:34,170
Wang Jianshan.

705
00:31:34,400 --> 00:31:34,930
Present.

706
00:31:35,550 --> 00:31:36,240
Xu Xiucai.

707
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:36,920
Here.

708
00:31:38,880 --> 00:31:40,140
