732
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:37,750
I...

733
00:32:37,920 --> 00:32:39,000
I'm...

734
00:32:39,080 --> 00:32:40,710
I-I'm called Niwei.

735
00:32:46,010 --> 00:32:48,010
