736
00:32:48,730 --> 00:32:50,450
This last one's name is Li San.

737
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:51,450
You fool.

738
00:32:52,040 --> 00:32:53,930
Isn't Niwei your nickname?

739
00:32:54,480 --> 00:32:55,480
Why did you give your nickname?

740
00:32:55,480 --> 00:32:56,990
The officer is asking for your full name.

741
00:32:56,990 --> 00:32:58,190
You should say Li San.

742
00:32:59,790 --> 00:33:00,240
Right.

743
00:33:00,350 --> 00:33:00,960
Right.

744
00:33:00,960 --> 00:33:02,480
I'm the third son

745
00:33:02,990 --> 00:33:03,920
of the Li family.

746
00:33:04,270 --> 00:33:05,270
I'm called Li San.

747
00:33:05,360 --> 00:33:06,560
My nickname is Niwei.

748
00:33:06,790 --> 00:33:08,830
My eldest brother is called Meiwei,

749
00:33:09,240 --> 00:33:11,640
a-and my second brother is called Chouwei.

750
00:33:13,830 --> 00:33:14,640
You're just

751
00:33:14,880 --> 00:33:16,440
as annoying as your name.

752
00:33:16,440 --> 00:33:17,680
Officer, that's right.

753
00:33:17,680 --> 00:33:19,270
He really is annoying.

754
00:33:21,590 --> 00:33:22,350
Annoying!

755
00:33:22,640 --> 00:33:23,920
Truly annoying.

756
00:33:24,620 --> 00:33:25,150
Alright.

757
00:33:25,510 --> 00:33:26,310
Let's leave it at that.

758
00:33:26,310 --> 00:33:26,720
Okay.

759
00:33:27,070 --> 00:33:27,530
See you.

760
00:33:27,880 --> 00:33:29,790
See you, Officer. Take care.

761
00:33:29,790 --> 00:33:30,250
Fall in!

762
00:33:31,270 --> 00:33:32,730
Bid the officer farewell.

763
00:33:33,030 --> 00:33:34,400
Farewell, Officer.

764
00:33:49,510 --> 00:33:50,030
Kejin,

765
00:33:50,480 --> 00:33:51,480
you were amazing.

766
00:33:51,830 --> 00:33:53,840
You insisted on helping the three of them.

767
00:33:53,840 --> 00:33:54,790
In just this short time,

768
00:33:54,790 --> 00:33:56,390
I spent five silver dollars.

769
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:57,530
Sit down.

770
00:33:57,750 --> 00:33:58,410
Take a rest.

771
00:34:00,240 --> 00:34:01,770
You wrote this, didn't you?

772
00:34:03,400 --> 00:34:04,000
Xiuxiu,

773
00:34:04,330 --> 00:34:06,030
why didn't you write my name Tietou?

774
00:34:06,030 --> 00:34:07,140
Why call me Wan Yier?

775
00:34:07,140 --> 00:34:08,540
I almost didn't catch on.

776
00:34:09,030 --> 00:34:10,560
The names of the three of you

777
00:34:11,670 --> 00:34:13,800
all contain complicated characters.

778
00:34:13,880 --> 00:34:15,139
I just had a short time,

779
00:34:15,179 --> 00:34:16,620
so I wrote simple names.

780
00:34:18,150 --> 00:34:19,190
My sister is so clever

781
00:34:19,190 --> 00:34:21,110
and came up with this plan
to save you three.

782
00:34:21,110 --> 00:34:22,030
Thank her now.

783
00:34:22,510 --> 00:34:23,340
-Thank you, Xiuxiu.
-Thank you, Xiuxiu.

784
00:34:23,340 --> 00:34:24,150
Thank you, Xiu.

785
00:34:24,150 --> 00:34:24,550
Kejin,

786
00:34:25,280 --> 00:34:26,679
let's go look for Dajiao.

787
00:34:26,880 --> 00:34:27,610
Oh, right.

788
00:34:28,070 --> 00:34:29,580
Our names are on this register now.

789
00:34:29,580 --> 00:34:31,110
We can help look for him too.

790
00:34:31,320 --> 00:34:32,670
Let's go now.

791
00:34:33,060 --> 00:34:34,100
Dajiao!

