00:34:36,550 --> 00:34:37,280
Dajiao!

795
00:34:38,510 --> 00:34:39,400
Dajiao!

796
00:34:39,710 --> 00:34:40,800
-Dajiao!
-Dajiao!

797
00:34:40,800 --> 00:34:41,260
Xiuxiu.

798
00:34:41,800 --> 00:34:42,760
Searching like this isn't working.

799
00:34:42,760 --> 00:34:43,400
Let's do this:

800
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:45,110
you and Zhuzi go search the fields,

801
00:34:45,110 --> 00:34:45,920
and I'll go with Niwei

802
00:34:45,920 --> 00:34:47,190
to search the mountains.

803
00:34:47,190 --> 00:34:47,590
Hurry!

