00:35:11,830 --> 00:35:12,360
Xiu.

811
00:35:13,110 --> 00:35:14,310
This is Dajiao's hoe.

812
00:35:14,660 --> 00:35:15,230
It…

813
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:16,800
It is.

814
00:35:17,880 --> 00:35:19,680
He'd never leave his hoe behind.

815
00:35:19,760 --> 00:35:21,320
Could something bad have happened to him?

816
00:35:21,320 --> 00:35:22,110
Dajiao.

817
00:35:23,960 --> 00:35:24,800
Dajiao.

818
00:35:25,510 --> 00:35:27,670
Bros, have you seen Dajiao?

819
00:35:27,840 --> 00:35:28,630
No, no.

820
00:35:28,630 --> 00:35:29,230
No, no.

821
00:35:31,440 --> 00:35:32,230
Dajiao!

822
00:35:33,030 --> 00:35:34,110
Dajiao!

823
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:38,360
Guiyao.

824
00:35:39,210 --> 00:35:40,740
Help me send a message home.

825
00:35:41,320 --> 00:35:42,120
What message?

826
00:35:43,630 --> 00:35:44,630
I'm just joking.

827
00:35:44,850 --> 00:35:47,380
When I bought the goods just now,
I got it done.

828
00:35:47,840 --> 00:35:49,510
You've really sent a message for me?

829
00:35:49,510 --> 00:35:50,760
What? You don't trust me?

830
00:35:50,760 --> 00:35:51,440
No, no, no.

831
00:35:52,170 --> 00:35:54,650
I'm just afraid they'll worry too much.

832
00:35:55,170 --> 00:35:56,170
They, huh?

833
00:35:56,760 --> 00:35:58,220
