00:37:43,360 --> 00:37:44,760
They took anyone they saw.

868
00:37:44,760 --> 00:37:47,070
If you can lift a gun, you're taken.

869
00:37:47,510 --> 00:37:49,800
They even took Xuerui away.

870
00:37:51,550 --> 00:37:52,800
Maybe

871
00:37:53,280 --> 00:37:54,230
Dajiao

872
00:37:55,400 --> 00:37:56,880
has been taken too.

873
00:38:03,630 --> 00:38:05,320
How could this happen?

874
00:38:09,320 --> 00:38:11,230
We're in such terrible times.

875
00:38:15,510 --> 00:38:17,920
Don't worry. Dajiao is blessed.

876
00:38:18,590 --> 00:38:21,000
He has Grandpa Ox watching over him.

877
00:38:25,250 --> 00:38:26,440
Dajiao.

878
00:38:28,180 --> 00:38:29,580
My Dajiao.

879
00:38:46,030 --> 00:38:46,670
Madam.

880
00:38:58,070 --> 00:38:59,030
Mr. Ning.

881
00:38:59,590 --> 00:39:01,320
What are you playing at?

882
00:39:02,440 --> 00:39:04,040
I'm not playing at anything.

883
00:39:04,710 --> 00:39:06,710
I don't beat around the bush either.

884
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:08,800
I just have one question for you.

885
00:39:09,320 --> 00:39:11,920
What family rule of yours
did my daughter break

886
00:39:12,150 --> 00:39:13,480
that you kicked her out?

887
00:39:16,120 --> 00:39:17,770
What are you talking about?

888
00:39:18,590 --> 00:39:20,360
I've been sick these past few days.

889
00:39:20,360 --> 00:39:23,190
I had no idea Susu went back to you.

890
00:39:24,550 --> 00:39:26,440
Even if she was neglected,

891
00:39:26,880 --> 00:39:28,670
it was because I was ill.

892
00:39:29,050 --> 00:39:31,050
That's hardly a serious offense.

893
00:39:32,230 --> 00:39:34,070
All the neighbors are here.

894
00:39:34,070 --> 00:39:35,880
They all know how I usually

895
00:39:35,880 --> 00:39:37,290
treat Susu.

896
00:39:37,330 --> 00:39:40,120
Susu should know that very well too.

897
00:39:40,630 --> 00:39:42,430
Stop using illness as an excuse.

898
00:39:42,470 --> 00:39:43,800
In my house,

899
00:39:44,140 --> 00:39:46,140
my daughter was doted on

900
00:39:46,920 --> 00:39:48,710
as the apple of my eye.

901
00:39:49,400 --> 00:39:52,130
Yet in your house,
she's barely fed and cared for.

902
00:39:52,670 --> 00:39:54,470
If you couldn't provide for her,

903
00:39:55,230 --> 00:39:56,890
you should've said so openly.

904
00:39:59,840 --> 00:40:02,920
Let all the villagers know about it.

905
00:40:03,630 --> 00:40:06,320
If only things were like what you said.

906
00:40:08,150 --> 00:40:11,840
Your daughter truly is
the apple of your eye.

907
00:40:12,550 --> 00:40:13,710
Everyone knows

908
00:40:13,960 --> 00:40:15,510
how Susu was married

909
00:40:15,920 --> 00:40:17,190
into the Fei family.

910
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:19,580
It's common knowledge for miles around.

911
00:40:26,710 --> 00:40:28,030
I have my own way

912
00:40:28,030 --> 00:40:29,760
to handle my family affairs.

913
00:40:30,110 --> 00:40:32,240
No one else has any right to interfere.

914
00:40:32,710 --> 00:40:35,320
I also have my own way to rent my land.

915
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:38,530
Whether it's permanent tenancy
or whatever,

916
00:40:38,590 --> 00:40:40,510
I won't let anyone blackmail me.

917
00:40:41,230 --> 00:40:42,550
If you cross the line,

918
00:40:42,550 --> 00:40:44,800
someone will put you in your place.

919
00:40:46,030 --> 00:40:46,880
Now,

920
00:40:47,420 --> 00:40:49,820
sort out your own family matters first.

921
00:40:50,230 --> 00:40:51,030
Tell me,

922
00:40:51,400 --> 00:40:54,260
my daughter suffered a lot.
What are you going to do?

923
00:40:54,270 --> 00:40:55,270
What can I do?

924
00:40:56,170 --> 00:40:58,280
She should get out of the carriage,
go back in,

925
00:40:58,280 --> 00:40:59,610
and fulfill her duties.

926
00:41:00,260 --> 00:41:02,000
If she fulfills her duties,

927
00:41:02,150 --> 00:41:03,190
the Fei family

928
00:41:03,530 --> 00:41:05,390
will certainly not mistreat her.

929
00:41:06,400 --> 00:41:07,110
Xiaoqin.

930
00:41:08,190 --> 00:41:09,320
Help Young Mistress out of the carriage.

931
00:41:09,320 --> 00:41:09,800
Yes.

932
00:41:13,450 --> 00:41:15,380
Young Mistress, please come down.

933
00:41:15,600 --> 00:41:17,600
Don't get out until this is settled.

934
00:41:26,960 --> 00:41:27,760
Mr. Ning,

935
00:41:28,950 --> 00:41:30,110
you failed your duty

936
00:41:30,140 --> 00:41:32,270
with the permanent tenancy.

937
00:41:32,950 --> 00:41:35,070
You don't get to settle the score with me.

938
00:41:35,070 --> 00:41:35,870
Because it was

939
00:41:36,070 --> 00:41:37,530
not my fault to start with.

940
00:41:38,320 --> 00:41:39,400
If you hadn't provoked Tietou,

941
00:41:39,400 --> 00:41:40,800
I wouldn't have lost this round.

942
00:41:40,800 --> 00:41:42,760
If you don't make up for my loss,

943
00:41:42,790 --> 00:41:43,850
I won't let you off.

944
00:41:45,030 --> 00:41:46,290
How should I make it up?

945
00:41:47,400 --> 00:41:48,440
I have an idea.

946
00:41:49,480 --> 00:41:51,360
After everything that's happened,

947
00:41:51,360 --> 00:41:53,290
you should give Susu five mu of land

948
00:41:53,460 --> 00:41:55,140
as a good gesture

949
00:41:55,460 --> 00:41:57,720
to welcome her back to the Fei Residence.

950
00:42:02,590 --> 00:42:04,360
I must say, your daughter is

951
00:42:04,510 --> 00:42:05,840
quite precious indeed.

952
00:42:06,600 --> 00:42:09,330
One trip home
could earn her five mu of land.

953
00:42:10,070 --> 00:42:12,620
The hundreds of mu of land
left by your ancestors

954
00:42:12,620 --> 00:42:14,480
were all acquired in the same way?

955
00:42:15,260 --> 00:42:16,130
Take

956
00:42:16,590 --> 00:42:17,720
your daughter home.

957
00:42:18,920 --> 00:42:20,510
Xiaoqin, let's head back in.

958
00:42:20,510 --> 00:42:21,000
Yes.

959
00:42:21,550 --> 00:42:22,230
Susu.

960
00:42:25,710 --> 00:42:26,440
Xiuxiu.

961
00:42:27,800 --> 00:42:28,360
Susu,

962
00:42:28,760 --> 00:42:29,400
Xiuxiu.

963
00:42:29,710 --> 00:42:30,440
Come with me.

964
00:42:31,760 --> 00:42:32,290
Careful.

965
00:42:35,070 --> 00:42:37,320
You're just arguing
for your own interests.

966
00:42:37,320 --> 00:42:38,450
Aren't you ashamed?

967
00:42:39,320 --> 00:42:41,850
Has anyone considered
my sister's feelings?

968
00:42:41,850 --> 00:42:44,250
And you call yourselves heads of families.

969
00:42:44,480 --> 00:42:46,240
You don't need to push her to each other.

970
00:42:46,240 --> 00:42:47,500
She's leaving with me.

971
00:42:47,850 --> 00:42:48,380
Let's go.

972
00:42:53,540 --> 00:42:54,710
I'm going back in.

973
00:42:58,960 --> 00:42:59,590
Mrs. Fei.

974
00:43:00,890 --> 00:43:01,400
Close the door.

975
00:43:01,400 --> 00:43:02,360
We're not finished here.
